.DT
fix_string
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
fix_string

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
fix_string -  This method handles the conversersions for the colour mapping which is done on Discworld.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs string fix_string(string str,
int width,
int indent,
mixed args ...)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^str%^RESET%^ - the string to do the conversion on
%^BOLD%^width%^RESET%^ - the width of the string
%^BOLD%^indent%^RESET%^ - the size of the indent
%^BOLD%^args%^RESET%^ - any other arguments
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the fixed up string
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/events.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method handles the conversersions for the colour mapping which is
done on Discworld.  This also does octarine message expansion, if the
keyword %\^OCTARINE:message%\^ is embeded into a string then the
inside section will be replaced with a blank string if the player
cannot see octarine messages.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
efun::terminal_colour()

.EP

